 ， F$ ，且与 $A D$ 只有一个交点，求圆形通道的周长 $\\qquad$ . (精确到 $0.01)$\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-118.jpg?height=318&width=304&top__y=889&top__x=299","line":2324},{"title":"|401x429","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-161.jpg?height=429&width=401&top__y=982&top__x=468","line":3169,"embedded":true},{"title":"50,60$ ) 内的人数为 16 ，则下列结论正确的是（）\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-185.jpg?height=435&width=618&top__y=1781&top__x=296","line":3666}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"19gd1oy","at":1769671094802}},"smart_blocks:01-数学教学/讲义/XDF讲义/FY25 高三数学秋季【行远班教材】3.0.md#目录": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.04544147,-0.00868611,0.07516135,0.02062725,0.03418786,-0.01426426,-0.06779543,0.04715706,0.03133813,0.05262285,0.03049168,-0.07539813,0.03281031,0.00516022,0.00628131,-0.00893285,-0.0220245,-0.02755723,-0.04359509,-0.01561054,0.12574373,-0.02293876,-0.00383679,-0.05626741,0.05831546,0.05988898,0.00523046,-0.08706509,-0.01809111,-0.19994739,-0.00459123,0.08587371,0.06630164,0.02324227,0.02616754,-0.0497724,-0.0074903,0.07284891,-0.01089551,0.04846812,0.0180834,0.07508217,0.01021838,0.0117119,-0.00406355,-0.06952246,-0.06677225,-0.02190301,0.03263296,-0.03279198,-0.04757222,-0.03034436,0.01028346,0.0408907,-0.03317606,0.01778306,0.04427155,0.00462649,0.02417988,0.03658107,0.0124404,0.0032647,-0.23557669,0.0469812,0.06197282,-0.01661188,-0.01517158,-0.0378636,0.02650648,0.0777824,-0.02707445,-0.00407626,0.00769171,0.01151468,-0.00601111,-0.02420029,0.00213753,-0.07910998,-0.02350868,-0.05859955,-0.035452,0.08567885,-0.04746383,-0.00101445,-0.01284826,0.04995715,0.00478371,-0.08446409,-0.00297811,-0.01224262,-0.00042244,-0.02468482,-0.02836761,0.02465788,-0.06956794,-0.04066858,0.00637238,0.00711687,-0.01096665,0.07759281,-0.03863182,0.00515875,0.04169015,-0.0002375,-0.03256992,0.0393387,-0.0038